{"tid":508860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[369] 黑的司機平安夜劏客 山頂落中環收$200衰咗","createTime":"2017-12-24T16:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T13:34:09.000Z","uid":42820,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff5e4c57147c3ee5fb30c65edcf1cd2ab8fa262","tid":508860,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"平安夜市民狂歡，警方於遊客眾多的山頂區，進行打擊的士司機濫收車資的行動。其間警方派出一男一女警員喬裝遊客，在山頂廣場截乘一輛的士前往中環機鐵站，司機開價收取200元車資，較合理車費約70元，多收近2倍。當的士抵步後司機收取車資，警員隨即表露身份，拘捕涉嫌濫收車資的61歲姓尹的士司機。警方指打擊行動將會通宵進行。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171224&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57623475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171224%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57623475&d=HL%2FrXwgy5U97G3dfGkx76L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=839fd196\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171224%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57623475&h=af06f67b\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171224&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57623475</a>"},{"pid":"f4d705208eb58d848e21e485f1270b26251fb257","tid":508860,"uid":22675,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"黑的遇黑警"},{"pid":"315089a025a3351e04f9bc07c6a55246d7c67291","tid":508860,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":59,"score":-59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c75d36ed647029c7e094cdb572d8d1258f3faa2","tid":508860,"uid":82474,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"315089a025a3351e04f9bc07c6a55246d7c67291","tid":508860,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":59,"score":-59,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"約70"},{"pid":"26457b